#. type: multicols*
#: sections/heroes.tex:77
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\pagetarget{Herocard}{\\subheader{Hero Board Anatomy}}\\index{Hero Board/Card}\n"
"\\hspace*{0.3em}\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
"  \\node (board) [inner sep=0] {\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\cards/hero.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{board}\n"
"    \\draw (0.72, 0.92) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.6, 0.85) node {\\encircle{2}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.92, 0.92) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.9) node {\\encircle{4}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.46, 0.7) node {\\encircle{5}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.6, 0.7) node {\\encircle{6}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.74, 0.7) node {\\encircle{7}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.88, 0.7) node {\\encircle{8}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.55, 0.5) node {\\encircle{9}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.85, 0.5) node {\\encircle{10}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.28, 0.25) node {\\encircle{11}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"\\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"\\begin{enumerate}[itemsep=0pt, leftmargin=1.5em]\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Name} – The Hero's name.\n"
"    Used for identification.\n"
"    Has no gameplay effect.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Class} – The Hero's class.\n"
"    Has no gameplay effect.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Type} – The Hero's type (Might \\svg[12]{might} or Magic \\svg{magic}).\n"
"    Determines the amount of \\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{Magic Arrow} Spells in your Starting Deck (1 or 2 respectively).\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Faction Color} – Reminder for the color of the Faction's Cubes and miniatures.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Attack}\\index{Attack!Hero} – Number of \\wikilink{statistics/attack}{Attack} cards in your Starting Deck.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Defense}\\index{Defense!Hero} – Number of \\wikilink{statistics/defense}{Defense} cards in your Starting Deck.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Power}\\index{Power} – Number of \\wikilink{statistics/power}{Power} cards in your Starting Deck.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Knowledge}\\index{Knowledge} – Number of \\wikilink{statistics/knowledge}{Knowledge} cards in your Starting Deck.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Starting Ability} – Reminder for the unique Ability card the Hero starts with.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Hero Specialty} – Reminder for the Specialty cards the Hero adds to their Deck at the start of the game and after specific Level ups.\n"
"    Each Hero has three Specialty cards.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Level Tracker} – Whenever a Main Hero gains 1 or more Experience \\svg{experience}, move the Cube that number of steps on this track.\n"
"    When the Cube reaches the next slot on the upper row, the Hero gains a Level.\n"
"\\end{enumerate}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\pagetarget{Herocard}{\\subheader{英雄面板结构}}\\index{英雄面板/牌}\n"
"\\hspace*{0.3em}\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
"  \\node (board) [inner sep=0] {\\includegraphics[width=\\linewidth]{\\cards/hero.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{board}\n"
"    \\draw (0.72, 0.92) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.6, 0.85) node {\\encircle{2}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.92, 0.92) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.9) node {\\encircle{4}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.46, 0.7) node {\\encircle{5}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.6, 0.7) node {\\encircle{6}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.74, 0.7) node {\\encircle{7}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.88, 0.7) node {\\encircle{8}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.55, 0.5) node {\\encircle{9}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.85, 0.5) node {\\encircle{10}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.28, 0.25) node {\\encircle{11}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"\\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"\\begin{enumerate}[itemsep=0pt, leftmargin=1.5em]\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{名称}——该英雄的名称。%\n"
"    用于识别。%\n"
"    没有游戏效果。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{职业}——该英雄的职业。%\n"
"    \\mbox{没有游戏效果}。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{类型}——该英雄的类型（力量\\svg[12]{might}或魔法\\svg{magic}）。%\n"
"    决定你的初始牌堆中\\wikilink{spells/magic_arrow}{魔法箭}法术的数量（分别为1或2）。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{阵营颜色}——\\mbox{该阵营方块和模型的颜色。}\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{攻击}\\index{攻击!英雄}——\\mbox{你的初始牌堆中\\wikilink{statistics/attack}{攻击}牌的数量。}\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{防御}\\index{防御!英雄}——\\mbox{你的初始牌堆中\\wikilink{statistics/defense}{防御}牌的数量。}\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{魔法威力}\\index{魔法威力}——你的初始牌堆中\\wikilink{statistics/power}{魔法威力}牌的数量。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{知识}\\index{知识}——\\mbox{你的初始牌堆中\\wikilink{statistics/knowledge}{知识}牌的数量。}\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{初始能力}——提醒该英雄开局拥有的独特能力牌。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{英雄特长}——提醒该英雄在游戏开始时以及特定等级提升后加入其牌堆的特长牌。%\n"
"    每位英雄有三张特长牌。\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{等级轨道}——每当主英雄获得1点或更多经验\\svg{experience}时，将方块在此轨道上移动相应步数。%\n"
"    当方块到达上排的下一个格位时，该英雄获得1个等级。\n"
"\\end{enumerate}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/heroes.tex:87
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\pagetarget{Level}{\\subheader{Level Effects}}\n"
"Main Heroes always start each Scenario at Level I\\index{Level} and may Level up by gaining Experience \\svg{experience}.\n"
"The most common sources of gaining Experience are the \\pagelink{Treasure Die}{Treasure Die \\svg{treasure}} and \\pagelink{Combatexperience}{Combat}.\n"
"Each new Level up requires \\textbf{2 Experience}.\n"
"When a Main Hero reaches a new Level, resolve the effects of the Level up immediately.\n"
"Gaining Experience at Level VII has no effect.\\par\n"
"The Level Tracker on your Hero Board shows the following effects:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\pagetarget{Level}{\\subheader{等级效果}}\n"
"主英雄总是在每个剧本开始时处于等级I\\index{等级}，并可以通过获得经验\\svg{experience}来升级。%\n"
"获得经验最常见的来源是\\pagelink{Treasure Die}{宝物骰\\svg{treasure}}和\\pagelink{Combatexperience}{战斗}。%\n"
"每次升级都需要\\textbf{2点经验}。%\n"
"当主英雄达到新等级时，立即结算升级的效果。%\n"
"在等级VII获得经验没有效果。\\par\n"
"你英雄面板上的等级轨道显示以下效果：\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: sections/heroes.tex:100
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item The Cube's position shows your Main Hero's current Level and amount of Experience gained.\n"
"  \\item At Levels \\herolevel{II}, \\herolevel{III}, \\herolevel{V}, and \\herolevel{VII} (marked with silver Roman numerals on the tracker), \\pagelink{Playerdecks}{Search~(2) the Ability Deck} and add the chosen card to your hand.\n"
"  \\item At Levels \\herolevel{I}, \\herolevel{IV}, and \\herolevel{VI} (marked in gold), gain the corresponding \\pagelink{Specialty}{Specialty card} and add it to your hand.\n"
"    Your first Specialty card is typically gained before the game starts.\n"
"  \\item Each time you reach a new Hand Limit \\svg{hand} slot, your Hand Limit increases from that point on (4 \\textrightarrow{} 5 \\textrightarrow{} 6 \\textrightarrow{} 7).\n"
"  \\item \\pagetarget{Expert Effect Markers}{}Each time you reach an Expert Effects \\svg{expert} slot, you may play one additional card for its Expert Effect per Round (up to a maximum of 3 at Level~\\herolevel{VI}).\n"
"    \\begin{expansion}[before skip balanced=0.3em,]{stretchgoals2}\n"
"      You can use Expert Effect Markers to track the usage of Expert Effects.\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/expert_effect_markers.png}\n"
"    \\end{expansion}\n"
"\\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item 方块的位置显示你的主英雄当前的等级和已获得的经验值。\n"
"  \\item 在等级 \\herolevel{II}、\\herolevel{III}、\\herolevel{V} 和 \\herolevel{VII}（在轨道上以银色罗马数字标记）时，\\pagelink{Playerdecks}{搜寻~(2)能力牌堆}，并将所选牌加入你的手牌。\n"
"  \\item 在等级 \\herolevel{I}、\\herolevel{IV} 和 \\herolevel{VI}（以金色标记）时，获得对应的\\pagelink{Specialty}{特长牌}，并将其加入你的手牌。\n"
"    你的第一张特长牌通常在游戏开始前获得。\n"
"  \\item 每当你到达一个新的手牌上限 \\svg{hand} 栏位时，你的手牌上限从此提高（4 \\textrightarrow{} 5 \\textrightarrow{} 6 \\textrightarrow{} 7）。\n"
"  \\item \\pagetarget{Expert Effect Markers}{}每当你到达一个专家效果 \\svg{expert} 栏位时，每轮你可以额外打出一张牌以使用其专家效果（最多为等级~\\herolevel{VI} 时的3张）。\n"
"    \\begin{expansion}[before skip balanced=0.3em,]{stretchgoals2}\n"
"      你可以使用专家效果标记来追踪专家效果的使用情况。\\par\n"
"      \\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\images/expert_effect_markers.png}\n"
"    \\end{expansion}\n"
"\\end{itemize}"
